org.xflatdb.xflat

Interface Cursor<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Iterable<T>

    public interface Cursor<T>
extends java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    A Cursor is an Iterable that maintains references to a resource, and must be closed in a finally block. It can also be used in a Java 7 try-with-resources.
